{"tid":1297451,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"鄉下係寶安縣其實係咪即係香港人","createTime":"2019-07-08T15:44:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T20:59:02.000Z","uid":74858,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"930203555768041908c377dc7e05457f8aee639e","tid":1297451,"uid":74858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:44:49.000Z","msg":"d人成日話你祖先咪又係游水落黎<br />\n問返我阿爺係寶安縣人<br />\n而舊時寶安縣係包埋香港深圳<br />\n所以舊底香港人會寫自己廣東寶安人<br />\n不過阿爺死咗 老豆老母香港出世 又喺元朗分到地 (阿爺有地但唔係原居民丁地， 唔知點解有) <br />\n其實我算唔算香港原居民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44a3d65461109f0778a04cd86ded0c59d992f4c","tid":1297451,"uid":44391,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:51:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60692517bfef7cc3f7fad828939fb466ee203329","tid":1297451,"uid":4964,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T15:53:36.000Z","msg":"香港人唔玩落後嘅血統論<br />\n中國國籍法嘅中國血統係毫無邏輯"},{"pid":"5c7f2fe9a61913c614c6a9a0770bdcc496f0cb34","tid":1297451,"uid":48149,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:03:10.000Z","msg":"只要肯融入香港 保衛香港 唔做蝗蟲 就係香港人<br />\n理撚得你係咩種族<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b678f886d1f15d8e97dcba287e6b9d9102960450","tid":1297451,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T16:05:52.000Z","msg":"鄉下係九龍 其實係咪即係旺角人"},{"pid":"b31ba4c135bee9cd8d5d070a4910688337b3ebf3","tid":1297451,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T17:32:47.000Z","msg":"咪垃圾黃種人 分咁細托柒"},{"pid":"fcd841c721086b689b02f1bb769a5e783ea6568e","tid":1297451,"uid":173852,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:59:02.000Z","msg":"有地唔出奇<br />\n60定70年代前香港人好似可以向政府申請批地<br />\n後來改左 要<strong>「咸豐」</strong>年間就住係度既人先申請得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n(「咸豐年前既事」依個成語，大約係咁樣黎)"}]}